Manuals
    man - system reference manuals
        Example
            man <COMMAND>
        Example
            man <CONF_FILE>
        Example
            man <DAEMON>
        Example
            man -k <SEARCH TEXT>
        Example
            man hier  # print description of directories hierarchy of the host machine

    whatis - one-line manual
        Example
            whatis <COMMAND>

    whereis - system file location (binary, source manual)
        Example
            whatis <COMMAND>

    mandb - update local manuals

